TEXT.TITLE: WESTERN HEALTH <WHP> PRESIDENT RESIGNS
TEXT.BODY: Western Health Plans Inc said Douglas C. Werner has resigned as president and chief executive officer to pursue other business opportunities. It said executive vice president Ray Mendoza will serve as interim chief executive. Reuter
